{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The iTunes affiliate program offers a number of powerful tools which you can use to add rich media and promotional links within your app or on the web. Start with an overview of the iTunes affiliate program and see how simple it is to get started linking to iTunes content. Dive deeper and learn how to use the advanced APIs and Services like Search, EPF, LinkMaker, and Web iMix to quickly and easily link to relevant content from the iTunes store."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc12-603-tools-services-and-apis-for-itunes-affiliate-program-marketing"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12-603-Tools-Services-and-APIs-for-iTunes-Affiliate-Program-Marketing"},"metadata":{"title":"Tools, Services, and APIs for iTunes Affiliate Program Marketing","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC12","role":"sampleCode"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/603\/"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"sections":[],"references":{"WWDC12-Icon.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC12-Icon.png","v